        <section class="segment-opener" data-uuid="04e0dcfcfa6943cc886dc8900598f498">
            <article data-uuid="aec2d28506b147e287323bc51082c5d5">
                <h4 data-uuid="56b20110b7e3413986157ee62117cd72">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="52e1046cf6634830afcc757ee49a3702">Christopher Columbus sailed across the Atlantic Ocean and reached a continent that was previously unknown to him.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="24a2fd95539f40cc95df37297605a11c">Columbus Sails across the Atlantic</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="980d4c4b246d47efaa84b83e3f8e023c"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
        <section class="graphic-organizer-prompt " data-uuid="f683c0029f674c7a8770d7591569e3ba">
            <div class="go-prompt-bottom-bar" data-uuid="c29291e2ab8241b6b5c8b6d6bb6b60cd">
                <p data-uuid="5095acd2931d4794993afa38969874fc">As you read, use the graphic organizer to take notes about the voyages of European explorers and their important results.</p>
            </div>
